19. gxf3 a6 {Orlov,N (2285)-Liberman,E (2159) Samara 2012 0-1 (48)}) 5... Ne5
6. Nxe5 dxe5 7. f3 Bd7 8. e4 e6 9. Be3 Be7 10. Qd2 O-O 11. O-O-O exd5 12. exd5
a6 13. c5 Ne8 14. Bc4 b5 15. Bb3 Bf5 16. g4 Bg6 17. Ne4 Bxe4 18. fxe4 a5 19.
Rdf1 {Balazs,I (2175)-Lenart,E (2221) Hungary 2005 0-1 (54)}) (4... a6 5. d5
Na5 6. e4 c5 7. a3 Qc7 8. Be3 Bd7 9. Nd2 Ng4 10. Bf4 g5 11. Bxg5 b5 12. cxb5 c4
13. Be2 Ne5 14. bxa6 Rg8 15. Be3 Rxg2 16. b4 cxb3 17. Nb5 Qb8 18. a7 Qxb5 19.
Bxb5 {Nguyen,C (2366)-Gervasio,R (2332) Paris 2003 1-0 (34)}) 5. e4 e5 6. d5 {
White threatens to win material: d5xc6} Nb4 (6... Ne7 7. Qb3 b6 8. Be2 $14) 7.
a3 $16 Na6 8. b4 c6 (8... g6 $5 $16) 9. dxc6 $18 bxc6 10. c5 Qc8 $2 (10... Nb8
$142 11. Bc4 a5 $18) 11. cxd6 Nb8 (11... Bg4 {doesn't get the bull off the ice}
12. Qd3 Bxf3 13. gxf3 $18 (13. Qxf3 $6 Nb8 $18) (13. Qxa6 $6 {is much worse}
Bxe4 14. Nxe4 Nxe4 $16)) 12. Be2 (12. Nxe5 $142 {keeps an even firmer grip} Be6
13. Bf4 Nbd7 $18) 12... a5 13. Bb2 (13. Na4 $142 {and White can already relax}
Qd8 14. Be3 $18) 13... c5 $4 {terrible, but what else could Black do to save
the game?} (13... axb4 14. Na4 Qd8 15. axb4 Nxe4 16. Bxe5 Bf5 $18) 14. b5 c4 (
14... Be6 {is not much help} 15. Nxe5 Qd8 16. Nf3 Qxd6 17. Qxd6 Bxd6 18. e5 $18
) 15. Nxe5 Be6 16. a4 (16. Qd4 {keeps an even firmer grip} Qd8 17. Nxc4 Bxc4
18. Bxc4 Qxd6 $18) 16... Nbd7 (16... Qc5 {there is nothing better in the
position} 17. Nf3 Bxd6 $18) 17. Nc6 g6 (17... Nb8 {does not improve anything}
18. e5 Nxc6 19. bxc6 $18) 18. e5 Ng4 (18... Nxe5 {desperation} 19. Nxe5 Bg7 $18
) 19. Bxg4 Bxg4 20. Qxg4 Nxe5 21. Qxc8+ Rxc8 22. Nxe5 Bxd6 23. Nc6 Bb4 24. O-O
Bc5 25. Ne4 Bf8 26. Bxh8 (26. Nf6#) 26... Kd7 27. Rad1+ Ke6 (27... Kc7 {
a fruitless try to alter the course of the game} 28. Be5+ Kb6 29. Rd7 Rxc6 30.
Bb8 Rc7 31. Bxc7+ Kb7 32. Bxa5+ Kb8 33. Rd8+ Kb7 34. Rxf8 f5 35. Rd1 fxe4 36.
Rd7#) 28. Ng5+ Kf5 29. Rd5+ Kg4 30. h3+ Kh5 31. Nxf7+ Kh4 (31... g5 {is no
salvation} 32. Rxg5+ Kh4 33. Nd4 c3 34. Nf5#) 32. Bf6+ (32. Bf6+ g5 33. Rxg5
Rxc6 34. Kh2 Rxf6 35. g3#) (32. Kh2 Bd6+ 33. g3+ Bxg3+ 34. fxg3#) 1-0

