a6 {Secures b5} 11. e5 dxe5 12. Nxe5 Bd6 13. Nxc6 bxc6 {White has a very
active position} 14. Be3 Bb7 (14... Be6 15. Bxe6 fxe6 16. Bd4 $11) 15. Qb3 {
