White has an active position} (16. Bd4 $5 c5 17. Bxf6 gxf6 18. Ne4 Bxe4 19.
Rxe4 $14) 16... Nd7 $14 17. Nc3 (17. Bd3 c5 $14) 17... c5 $11 18. Rad1 Rb8 19.
Qc2 Nf6 (19... Ne5 $142 {and Black could well hope to play on} 20. Bd5 Rd8 $11)
20. Bxh6 $1 $16 {Deflection: f7} gxh6 $4 {simply worsens the situation} (20...
Re8 $142 $16) 21. Qg6+ Kh8 22. Qxf6+ Kg8 23. Re3 Qd8 (23... h5 {does not help
