$19) 39. Kg1 Nd3 (39... Be6 {makes it even easier for Black} 40. Nf5 $19) 40.
Rf3 (40. Rd4 Bb7 41. g4 $19) 40... Bb7 41. Rf6 (41. Nf1 {is not much help} Bxf3
42. Nxd2 Bd5 $19) 41... Re6 42. Nc4 (42. Rxe6 {doesn't change anything anymore}
fxe6 43. Rb1 Nxc5 $19) 42... Rde2 (42... Ra2 43. f3 Rxa1+ 44. Kg2 Re2+ 45. Kh3
Nf2+ 46. Kg2 Ne4+ 47. Kh3 Bc8+ 48. Rf5 h5 49. fxe4 Rh1#) 43. Rxe6 Rxe6 44. Nd6
Bc6 (44... Ba8 {keeps an even firmer grip} 45. Nf5 $19) 45. Rb1 (45. Nf5 {
doesn't do any good} Re5 46. Nd4 Rxc5 47. Nxc6 Rxc6 $19) 45... Nxc5 46. Rb8+ (
46. Nf5 {is not the saving move} Be4 47. Rc1 Nxa4 $19 (47... Bxf5 $143 48. Rxc5
Be4 49. Kh2 $19)) 46... Kg7 (46... Kh7 $142 {seems even better} 47. Rb1 Rxd6
$19) 47. Nc4 (47. Nf5+ {is still a small chance} Kf6 48. Ne3 $19) 47... Re1+
48. Kh2 Rh1# 0-1

