2. Nc3 Bc5 3. Nf3 Nc6 4. g3 Nf6 5. Bg2 O-O 6. O-O d6 7. d3 Be6 8. a3 a6 9. b4
Ba7 10. Rb1 $146 (10. Nd2 Rb8 11. Rb1 Ne7 12. a4 Qd7 13. b5 Bh3 14. Ba3 h6 15.
e3 Bxg2 16. Kxg2 Bc5 17. Bxc5 dxc5 18. Nf3 Qe6 19. e4 c6 20. Qb3 Rbd8 21. bxa6
bxa6 22. Qc2 Ng6 23. Ng1 Rb8 24. a5 Nd7 {Carlsen,M (2802)-Adams,M (2723)
London 2010 1-0 (49)}) 10... Rb8 11. Qc2 Qd7 12. Ng5 Bf5 13. Nge4 (13. e3 $142
$11) 13... Bd4 $4 {weakening the position} (13... Nxe4 $142 {saving the game}
14. dxe4 Nd4 $11) 14. Nxf6+ $18 gxf6 15. Nd5 Qd8 16. Bh6 Re8 17. e3 Ba7 18. Qe2
(18. b5 Na5 19. f4 axb5 20. fxe5 Rxe5 21. Rxb5 c6 22. Rxf5 Rxf5 $18) 18... Bg6
(18... Kh8 19. f4 $18) 19. Rbd1 Ne7 (19... Kh8 20. h4 Ne7 21. Nxe7 (21. Nxf6
$143 Nf5 22. Nxe8 Nxh6 $16) 21... Qxe7 22. e4 $18) 20. Nxf6+ Kh8 21. Nxe8 Nf5 (
21... Qxe8 {a fruitless try to alter the course of the game} 22. Bg5 $18) 22.
Nxc7 $1 {the knock-out blow} Qxc7 23. Bg5 1-0

