material: b5xc6} Nb8 (7... Ne7 8. e3 $14) 8. Qa4 (8. e3 $142 $16) 8... Bd7 $2 (
8... Nbd7 9. Bb2 $11) 9. Ne5 (9. Nxd4 $142 {with excellent chances for White}
Qb6 10. Nf3 $18) 9... Qc7 $14 10. Nxd7 Nbxd7 11. d3 {Secures e4} Nb6 {Black
threatens to win material: Nb6xa4} 12. Qb3 Bd6 13. a4 Rd8 14. Bg5 Be7 (14...
Nbd7 15. Nd2 $14) 15. Nd2 Nbd7 16. a5 b6 (16... Ng4 $5 17. Bxe7 Kxe7 $16) 17.
