8. Bxf6 $18 exf6 9. cxd5 Nb4 10. Bb5+ Bd7 11. Qe2+ Be7 $4 {leading to a quick
end} (11... Qe7 $142 12. Bxd7+ Kxd7 $18) 12. d6 O-O (12... Bc6 {praying for a
miracle} 13. Bxc6+ bxc6 14. dxe7 Qxe7 15. Qxe7+ Kxe7 $18) 13. dxe7 ({Not} 13.
Qxe7 Re8 14. O-O Rxe7 15. dxe7 Qxe7 $17) 13... Qxe7 14. Qxe7 Bxb5 15. Qxb4
Rfe8+ 16. Kd2 Bd7 17. Nd5 Kh8 18. Nc7 (18. Nxf6 $142 {and White can already
relax} a5 19. Qxb7 Reb8 20. Qxd7 Kg7 $18) 18... Rac8 19. Nxe8 Bxe8 20. Qf8# 1-0

